                <li>Support Groups and Counseling Services</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="vision">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>Our vision is to build a vibrant and resilient community where individuals can thrive and flourish in all
                aspects of their lives. By fostering connections, promoting wellness, and celebrating diversity, we
                aspire to create a stronger, more cohesive community for generations to come.</p>
        </section>
